 *   @file   adf4382.c
 *   @brief  Implementation of adf4382 Driver.
 *   @author Ciprian Hegbeli (ciprian.hegbeli@analog.com)
 *   @author Jude Osemene (jude.osemene@analog.com)
********************************************************************************
